nditions of these systems and will examine the early phases of the\nmerger to determine its viability for triggering a thermonuclear detonation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2015 20:26:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Jan 2016 04:58:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-16"}
