 area of the magnetization that can be\nused to quantify how far the system is from equilibrium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Dec 2015 07:45:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 11:31:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-30"}
